    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >   Welcome to Mikoshi!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of the retro cyberpunk world of Mikoshi!  A unique combination of dynamic gameplay requiring skill and precision, a deep story that reveals the secrets of the world and characters. The vibrant visual style, neon aesthetic and soulful soundtrack create a unique atmosphere of 1990's games. Jump, fight, hack into systems, control various vehicles and drones! Uncover the conspiracy, find the lost crystals of the Mikoshi Temple! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823090/extras/ef654e681d536cd9af59205576b59583.poster.avif?t=1736950689\" width=560 height=315 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823090/extras/ef654e681d536cd9af59205576b59583.webm?t=1736950689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1990's cyberpunk platformer </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > High quality graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each level is a unique location</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;Comics&quot;-style game Trailers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bonus levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Epic boss battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Gain XP to open new perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Secrets hidden throughout</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hacking enemy drones, control it, driving different vehicles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Interesting story, dialogs, characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hardcore gameplay challenges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
